<p style={{ marginBottom: "0.4em" }}><strong>Values</strong></p>

<table>
<thead><tr><th>Value</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>ASC</td>
<td>

</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>DESC</td>
<td>
<p>Specifies a descending order for a given <code>orderBy</code> argument.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
